children.subject: It's usually listed as "CS 399: Professional Preparation: Supervised Teaching of Computer Science"
what class are the 2 p/np units listed as?

history.content:
The Web Design DeCal will be offered again for Fall 2021, and we’re looking for TAs to join the team! If you have any web design and development experience, we encourage you to apply at wdd.io/go/ta-fa21 by next Friday, July 16th. You do not need to have taken the decal before, and you can check out more details of our decal on our website, http://wdd.io/.

Class will be held over Zoom on Tuesdays 7:00 - 8:30pm and Thursdays 6:30–8:00pm PT, where Tuesday will be a 1.5 hour lecture and Thursday will a half hour online staff meeting preceding the 1 hour lab. TA responsibilities include answering questions during class, running weekly labs, hosting office hours, and updating curriculum. Being a TA for WDD is extremely rewarding, and you can also receive two PNP units.

If you have any questions about the course or the TA app, feel free to post a follow-up or contact us at ask@wdd.io!
history.subject: Web Design DeCal Fall 2021 - Apply to be a TA!
